Dirt, sludge and limescale buildup over time can reduce the efficiency of your central heating system and effectively raise your heating bills. Power flushing may alleviate those issues.

## Checklist 

Look out for the following symptoms which indicate your heating system needs Power flushing.

1. Producing less heat than usual 
2. Slow to heat up 
3. Constant need to bleed radiators. 
4. Noisy Boiler 
5. Heating Pump fails regularly. 

